":0,"score":"5869924453","product_id":100039701,"comment_content":"<br>授人以鱼不如授人以渔，“捡豆子”这件事儿就是教我们自己“钓鱼”。好的老师会告诉你考点让你的分数有所谓的增加，像爱民老师这样的老师（我心目中最优秀的老师之一）会教给你如何独立去思考，以便自己能够独立找到隐藏在考点后面的秘密。所谓“懂”，我理解是建立自己的认知与思维模式的架构，无论是学习JavaScript还是任何东西都可以游刃有余。这个系列课程进行未半已然终身受益，感谢老师的辛勤付出。","like_count":1,"discussions":[{"author":{"id":1521669,"avatar":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/17/38/05/7beecd5d.jpg","nickname":"Aiming","note":"","ucode":"66292B32F9960A","race_medal":0,"user_type":2,"is_pvip":false},"reply_author":{"id":0,"avatar":"","nickname":"","note":"","ucode":"","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"discussion":{"id":68863,"discussion_content":"谢谢。^^.","likes_number":0,"is_delete":false,"is_hidden":false,"ctime":1575223675,"is_liked":false,"can_delete":false,"is_complain":false,"is_top":false,"parent_id":0,"ip_address":""},"score":2,"extra":"","child_discussion_number":0,"child_discussions":[]}]},{"had_liked":false,"id":156441,"user_name":"kittyE","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1025944,"ip_address":"","ucode":"B6F59C96498EAF","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/0f/a7/98/1491b4a3.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1574871922,"is_pvip":false,"replies":[{"id":"60094","content":"一是我对数学的兴趣起源于小学；二是这位小学数学老师非常好，值得尊敬；三是那本书中，所用到的数学知识，止于小学足矣。<br>:)","user_name":"作者回复","user_name_real":"Aiming","uid":"1521669","ctime":1574907993,"ip_address":"","comment_id":156441,"utype":1}],"discussion_count":1,"race_medal":0,"score":"5869839218","product_id":100039701,"comment_content":"老师，小学数学老师对您影响很大吗？","like_count":1,"discussions":[{"author":{"id":1521669,"avatar":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/17/38/05/7beecd5d.jpg","nickname":"Aiming","note":"","ucode":"66292B32F9960A","race_medal":0,"user_type":2,"is_pvip":false},"reply_author":{"id":0,"avatar":"","nickname":"","note":"","ucode":"","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"discussion":{"id":476109,"discussion_content":"一是我对数学的兴趣起源于小学；二是这位小学数学老师非常好，值得尊敬；三是那本书中，所用到的数学知识，止于小学足矣。\n:)","likes_number":0,"is_delete":false,"is_hidden":false,"ctime":1574907993,"is_liked":false,"can_delete":false,"is_complain":false,"is_top":true,"parent_id":0,"ip_address":""},"score":2,"extra":"{\"reply\":true,\"user_type\":2}","child_discussion_number":0,"child_discussions":[]}]},{"had_liked":false,"id":156416,"user_name":"佳民","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1000433,"ip_address":"","ucode":"A5626BAEC96945","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/0f/43/f1/3c69eb09.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1574868583,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"5869835879","product_id":100039701,"comment_content":"我对懂的理解是，能把握核心，洞察本质，例如每篇文章标题中的语句对应的原理是什么，又如这个专栏是编程语言层面知识，而不是工程使用的内容。我理解的懂吃是知道菜有哪些做法，为什么要这么做，以及应该配什么佐料和辅材。","like_count":1},{"had_liked":false,"id":340233,"user_name":"让时间说真话","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1387656,"ip_address":"","ucode":"5C86450864189F","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/15/2c/88/2a7fe1a9.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1648689259,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1648689259","product_id":100039701,"comment_content":"懂理解从两个角度，1：懂这门课讲的啥，不是教你怎么写代码，而是教你代码是啥？2：懂了这些代码语法写起代码来才会顺。","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":321022,"user_name":"明月","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1338736,"ip_address":"","ucode":"D6586156BF09CF","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/14/6d/70/25ba4287.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1636623360,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1636623360","product_id":100039701,"comment_content":"“懂”，我的理解更像是老师文中说的“架构能力”：知道味道产生的原因，甚至是发生了什么呀的化学反应。同样的食材还有没有可能产生其他的味道，其他的食材有没有可能产生当前的味道。当前的味道可以归类于哪一个味道体系下：偏甜、偏咸、偏辣等等。<br>即建立关于味道的体系，还能抽象出产生味道的诸多概念。","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":265746,"user_name":"仿生狮子","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1565909,"ip_address":"","ucode":"ECB2726F7E8F